1
00:00:16,140 --> 00:00:18,240
Medley of youth
Preložila Kiyo

2
00:00:38,220 --> 00:00:39,260
<i>Choi Jeong-Woo.</i>

3
00:00:39,260 --> 00:00:42,090
Ahoj, Deok-Won.
Ako sa máš?

4
00:00:42,660 --> 00:00:45,100
Dostal som od teba správu.

5
00:00:45,100 --> 00:00:47,870
Spomenul som si na teba,
keď som zálohoval fotky.

6
00:00:47,870 --> 00:00:49,330
Je to celkom vtipné.

7
00:00:51,800 --> 00:00:52,940
Čo máš nové?

8
00:00:52,940 --> 00:00:54,710
<i>Dokopy nič.</i>

9
00:00:54,710 --> 00:00:57,740
<i>Nejdú obchody, ťažko je.</i>

10
00:00:58,580 --> 00:01:00,010
<i>Má zajtra čas?</i>

11
00:01:03,450 --> 00:01:04,750
Som v práci.

12
00:01:05,320 --> 00:01:07,550
Ako učiteľovi na polovičnom
úväzku mi voľno nepreplatia.

13
00:01:08,850 --> 00:01:11,890
Odídem hneď, ako získam certifikát.

14
00:01:11,890 --> 00:01:14,260
<i>Zomrel dedko z potravín.</i>

15
00:01:17,900 --> 00:01:21,230
<i>Pohreb je v stredu ráno.
Mali by sme ísť.</i>

16
00:01:22,570 --> 00:01:24,500
<i>Volám, komu sa dá.</i>

17
00:01:28,040 --> 00:01:29,610
Dobre.

18
00:01:30,980 --> 00:01:34,150
Porozprávam sa so šéfkou
a nejako posuniem rozvrh.

19
00:01:35,850 --> 00:01:36,920
Dobre.

20
00:01:38,380 --> 00:01:39,450
Ahoj.

21
00:02:13,990 --> 00:02:16,960
<i>Pred desiatimi rokmi.{\i}</i>

22
00:02:27,770 --> 00:02:32,540
<i>...a v tichosti zaspia.</i>

23
00:02:37,910 --> 00:02:38,940
Zlé?

24
00:02:43,180 --> 00:02:44,320
Bolo to až také strašné?

25
00:02:45,950 --> 00:02:48,690
Nezachytil si srdcia divákov.

26
00:02:51,260 --> 00:02:52,290
Divákov?

27
00:03:23,920 --> 00:03:25,120
Mám ti pomôcť?

28
00:03:27,530 --> 00:03:30,900
Pomôžem ti s tou piesňou.

29
00:03:31,830 --> 00:03:32,960
Pomôžem.

30
00:04:02,490 --> 00:04:03,530
Počuj.

31
00:04:04,660 --> 00:04:05,700
No?

32
00:04:06,870 --> 00:04:10,230
Jeong-Woo, spievaš piesne aj na želanie?

33
00:04:11,500 --> 00:04:13,040
Jasné, akú by si chcela?

34
00:04:14,540 --> 00:04:15,940
Takú, čo ma rozveselí.

35
00:04:18,880 --> 00:04:22,080
Môžeš zaspievať niečo, čo ma rozveselí?

36
00:04:27,290 --> 00:04:29,120
Jasné, zaspievam.

37
00:05:06,590 --> 00:05:09,030
Choi Jeong-Woo, chalan,
ktorý si vie život užiť,

38
00:05:09,030 --> 00:05:11,360
sa stáva víťazom Národnej speváckej súťaže!

39
00:05:12,430 --> 00:05:13,560
Skáčte!

40
00:05:19,940 --> 00:05:22,810
<i>My nikoho nepodporujeme!</i>

41
00:05:22,810 --> 00:05:24,840
<i>Keď nekričíš, tak si slaboch!</i>

42
00:05:24,840 --> 00:05:30,980
<i>Žijem krásny a zomieram presne tak!{\i}</i>

43
00:05:30,980 --> 00:05:33,820
<i>Slzy mi nikdy nezastrú zrak!{\i}</i>

44
00:05:33,820 --> 00:05:37,190
<i>Tak sa správa pravý chlap!{\i}</i>

45
00:05:39,090 --> 00:05:42,260
<i>Nemá byť čo slabochom!{\i}</i>

46
00:05:42,260 --> 00:05:44,930
<i>Nechávaj si hrdosť{\i}</i>

47
00:05:45,630 --> 00:05:50,070
<i>Slzy netečú potokom!{\i}</i>

48
00:05:50,500 --> 00:05:51,970
[Pre súťažiacich v Národnej
speváckej súťaži 30 minút zdarma]

49
00:05:51,970 --> 00:05:53,470
<i>Zlé, zlé dievča!{\i}</i>

50
00:05:53,940 --> 00:05:55,610
-Hej.
-Čo?

51
00:05:55,610 --> 00:05:57,380
Yeok-Ho fakt príde?

52
00:05:57,380 --> 00:06:00,950
Určite.
Dnes si do vás nezačne.

53
00:06:00,950 --> 00:06:01,710
Fakt?

54
00:06:02,310 --> 00:06:05,120
Takže veľký Yeok-Ho sa ani nehne?

55
00:06:05,550 --> 00:06:08,220
Popravde, je to preto, že

56
00:06:08,220 --> 00:06:12,260
sa chce stať profi boxerom.

57
00:06:13,290 --> 00:06:15,560
Boxerom?
Fakt?

58
00:06:15,560 --> 00:06:16,590
Bude mať skúšku na licenciu.

59
00:06:17,060 --> 00:06:19,900
Preto sa s vami nesmie biť.

60
00:06:19,900 --> 00:06:22,100
Lebo by ho diskvalifikovali.

61
00:06:23,800 --> 00:06:24,970
Počkajte.

62
00:06:25,700 --> 00:06:28,570
Drž už hubu.

63
00:06:28,970 --> 00:06:31,010
Prečo to robíš?
Nemal by si.

64
00:06:34,450 --> 00:06:36,710
Tak nám pomôžte.

65
00:06:37,280 --> 00:06:38,750
-Dobre?
-Iste.

66
00:06:40,090 --> 00:06:41,150
Yeong-Bok.

67
00:06:56,000 --> 00:06:57,770
Čus, dlho sme sa nevideli.

68
00:06:59,070 --> 00:07:00,570
Skrýval si sa pred nami.

69
00:07:12,990 --> 00:07:15,390
Vráť bratom mangu.

70
00:07:18,220 --> 00:07:20,530
Toto je pre nich.

71
00:07:24,130 --> 00:07:26,400
Vravel si, že majú radi teokboki.

72
00:07:31,940 --> 00:07:33,440
To myslíš vážne?

73
00:07:34,140 --> 00:07:36,510
Takto sa k hosťom nespráva.

74
00:07:40,210 --> 00:07:43,110
Grizly, myslím, že čosi dlžíš aj nám.

75
00:07:47,720 --> 00:07:49,620
Bolo tak super.

76
00:07:50,760 --> 00:07:53,460
Odkedy som nastúpil na
strednú, nemám rád školu.

77
00:07:54,060 --> 00:07:56,930
No teraz je to super.

78
00:07:56,930 --> 00:07:58,830
Odkedy si sem prestúpil.

79
00:08:00,570 --> 00:08:02,900
Nepodlizuj sa mi teraz,
keď som zaplatil karaoke.

80
00:08:02,900 --> 00:08:05,100
Nie, myslím to vážne.

81
00:08:05,100 --> 00:08:07,570
Veľa sa toho zmenilo, odkedy si prišiel.

82
00:08:07,570 --> 00:08:10,740
Starší študenti aj predsedkyňa.

83
00:08:11,540 --> 00:08:13,180
Si hrdina.

84
00:08:13,950 --> 00:08:15,050
Hrdina Namilskej strednej.

85
00:08:21,650 --> 00:08:23,650
Žijem krásny a zomieram presne tak...

86
00:08:23,660 --> 00:08:24,720
Prestaň.

87
00:08:29,530 --> 00:08:30,560
Čo sa deje?

88
00:08:48,810 --> 00:08:50,750
Grizly sa nám teda zmenil.

89
00:08:50,750 --> 00:08:52,320
Vráť sa, kam patríš.

90
00:08:52,320 --> 00:08:54,250
Tak ty si športovec, hej?

91
00:08:55,950 --> 00:08:58,220
Dúfal si, že ťa necháme tak?

92
00:08:58,220 --> 00:09:00,460
Toto je za všetko, čo si nám urobil.

93
00:09:08,430 --> 00:09:09,470
Grizly?

94
00:09:11,940 --> 00:09:13,370
Prečo sa nechá?

95
00:09:14,210 --> 00:09:15,210
Neviem.

96
00:09:15,210 --> 00:09:17,740
Nestarajme sa do nich.
Proste zavolajme polišov.

97
00:09:17,740 --> 00:09:18,780
Počkaj.

98
00:09:19,910 --> 00:09:20,950
Čo?

99
00:09:29,960 --> 00:09:31,690
Si v pohode?
Prepáč.

100
00:09:31,690 --> 00:09:34,860
O chvíľu budeš mať skúšku na licenciu.
Šetri sa.

101
00:09:34,860 --> 00:09:36,730
Ukľudni sa.
Oddychuj.

102
00:09:43,900 --> 00:09:46,140
Mal by som mu pomôcť.

103
00:09:46,140 --> 00:09:48,210
Čo? Prečo?
Deok-Won!

104
00:09:49,610 --> 00:09:50,710
Prestaň!

105
00:09:54,210 --> 00:09:56,050
Aký debil to sem doliezol?

106
00:10:00,720 --> 00:10:01,850
Bastard jeden.

107
00:10:01,850 --> 00:10:03,220
Won-Il, poď sem.

108
00:10:04,520 --> 00:10:06,490
Čo to robíš?

109
00:10:07,060 --> 00:10:10,430
Veď sme sem len došli po mangu!

110
00:10:10,430 --> 00:10:13,430
Pohodlne sa usaď a uži si predstavenie.

111
00:10:13,430 --> 00:10:15,300
O čo ti ide, do riti?

112
00:10:15,730 --> 00:10:18,700
Yeok-Ho k nám nie je zlý.
Čo to s tebou je?

113
00:10:19,470 --> 00:10:21,010
Ty, ale hovor.

114
00:10:22,510 --> 00:10:26,180
Počuj, debil.
Je to kvôli Yang Ah-Yeong, však?

115
00:10:26,680 --> 00:10:28,850
Ide o to, že chodí s tým novým.

116
00:10:29,650 --> 00:10:32,880
Prečo si vybíjaš hnev na Yeok-Hovi?

117
00:10:32,880 --> 00:10:34,890
Tebe už úplne drbe?

118
00:10:38,760 --> 00:10:40,790
Páči sa ti byť jeho handrou?

119
00:10:41,790 --> 00:10:43,860
No hovor, kretén!

120
00:10:54,510 --> 00:10:56,040
Si taký debil.

121
00:11:02,780 --> 00:11:03,950
Čo to?

122
00:11:10,420 --> 00:11:12,920
<i>Vravel si, že majú radi teokboki.</i>

123
00:11:17,500 --> 00:11:18,600
Hej, Lee Won-Il.

124
00:11:29,010 --> 00:11:30,780
Už aj s tým prestaňte, debili!

125
00:11:33,610 --> 00:11:35,280
Zbláznil si sa?

126
00:11:38,680 --> 00:11:41,620
Okamžite všetci prestaňte.

127
00:11:42,520 --> 00:11:44,720
Prečo naňho idete všetci?

128
00:11:50,130 --> 00:11:53,000
Viem, že je ťažké sa
do tej prípravky dostať,

129
00:11:53,870 --> 00:11:56,230
ale skús mi o tom niečo nájsť.

130
00:11:56,230 --> 00:11:58,800
Áno, to ma zaujíma.

131
00:11:59,570 --> 00:12:03,440
Ah-Yeong je tu síce premiantka,
no toto nie je Seoul.

132
00:12:20,790 --> 00:12:25,260
<i>Na chvíľu som Grizlymu závidel.</i>

133
00:12:26,670 --> 00:12:27,730
<i>Nie.</i>

134
00:12:30,600 --> 00:12:32,240
<i>Len vyzeral dobre.</i>

135
00:12:34,170 --> 00:12:35,210
Stačí!

136
00:12:35,210 --> 00:12:36,610
Bolí to!

137
00:12:47,320 --> 00:12:48,520
No koho to tu máme?

138
00:12:49,090 --> 00:12:52,160
Prišiel si pomôcť Grizlymu?

139
00:12:53,260 --> 00:12:57,330
Myslíš si, že sem môžeš prísť?

140
00:12:57,330 --> 00:12:58,330
Čo je?

141
00:12:59,000 --> 00:13:00,500
Hore sa a bež mu pomôcť.

142
00:13:00,930 --> 00:13:04,300
Ak sa zraní, Ah-Yeong to neprežije.

143
00:13:08,070 --> 00:13:10,470
Čo?
Ty to nevieš?

144
00:13:13,080 --> 00:13:14,380
Ahá, jasné.

145
00:13:15,750 --> 00:13:20,250
Hej, oni predsa v škole
hrajú, že sa nepoznajú.

146
00:13:20,790 --> 00:13:22,920
Vieš ty vôbec,

147
00:13:22,920 --> 00:13:26,260
čo sa medzi ním a tvojou babou deje?

148
00:13:33,330 --> 00:13:35,500
Čo budeš teraz robiť?

149
00:13:47,050 --> 00:13:48,380
Yeok-Ho, si v pohode?

150
00:13:48,950 --> 00:13:50,280
Už stačí!

151
00:13:58,590 --> 00:13:59,620
Dosť!

152
00:14:01,560 --> 00:14:03,730
Prečo sa naňho kukáš?

153
00:14:05,300 --> 00:14:06,900
Čo budeš robiť?

154
00:14:06,900 --> 00:14:09,100
Nelez sem a vypadni.

155
00:15:39,060 --> 00:15:41,360
Mám zlomené okuliare.

156
00:15:41,360 --> 00:15:43,290
Debili.

157
00:15:47,330 --> 00:15:48,500
Šteňa.

158
00:15:49,370 --> 00:15:50,230
No?

159
00:15:50,900 --> 00:15:52,140
Prečo si sem prišiel?

160
00:15:54,170 --> 00:15:57,880
Roznášal som a videl vás cez plot.

161
00:15:59,040 --> 00:16:02,350
A rozhodol sa zapojiť?

162
00:16:03,080 --> 00:16:04,850
Si tak blbý, až to bolí.

163
00:16:06,450 --> 00:16:07,890
Čo tvoj kamoš?

164
00:16:14,360 --> 00:16:16,230
Nehraj sa na zlatého.

165
00:16:20,770 --> 00:16:22,730
Bože, krvácam.

166
00:16:24,540 --> 00:16:27,640
Hyung, nemali by sme ich zažalovať?

167
00:16:34,310 --> 00:16:38,280
<i>Vieš, Yeok-Ho nie je taký zlý.</i>

168
00:16:42,290 --> 00:16:44,020
<i>Si hrdina.</i>

169
00:16:44,720 --> 00:16:45,960
<i>Hrdina Namilskej strednej.</i>

170
00:17:08,080 --> 00:17:10,510
Deok-Won?
Čo to máš na tvári?

171
00:17:11,220 --> 00:17:12,380
To ti spravil Yeong-Bok?

172
00:17:13,020 --> 00:17:16,090
Nie, len som spadol z bicykla.

173
00:17:16,090 --> 00:17:18,020
No to určite.

174
00:17:19,190 --> 00:17:21,190
Jeong-Woo, pozri naňho.

175
00:17:21,690 --> 00:17:22,790
To má od Yeong-Boka.

176
00:17:24,360 --> 00:17:26,000
Yeong-Bok je taký kretén.

177
00:17:27,300 --> 00:17:29,270
Dajme mu riadnu príučku!

178
00:17:29,770 --> 00:17:31,600
Akú príučku?
Mám novinky.

179
00:17:32,500 --> 00:17:33,270
Posuň sa.

180
00:17:33,640 --> 00:17:36,770
Grizly sa v sobotu pobil s Farebným gangom.

181
00:17:37,410 --> 00:17:38,810
Zomrel niekto z Farebných?

182
00:17:38,810 --> 00:17:41,610
Nie, ževraj sa im Grizly úplne nechal.

183
00:17:41,610 --> 00:17:42,650
-To fakt?
-Hej.

184
00:17:42,650 --> 00:17:44,350
Ale pozri naňho.

185
00:17:44,820 --> 00:17:46,080
Čo sa ti stalo?

186
00:17:51,220 --> 00:17:52,960
Deok-Won.
Tá sobota...

187
00:17:52,960 --> 00:17:56,030
Ach, jasné.
Musím ísť do zborovne.

188
00:17:56,930 --> 00:18:01,970
Kto sa bije lepšie,
Yeong-Bok alebo Grizly?

189
00:18:01,970 --> 00:18:03,700
Jasné, že Grizly.

190
00:18:04,170 --> 00:18:07,640
Je to zázvorové.
Dobré na modriny.

191
00:18:12,940 --> 00:18:14,110
Dobré ráno.

192
00:18:14,450 --> 00:18:15,810
Nevieš ísť rýchlejšie?

193
00:18:17,780 --> 00:18:18,780
Na.

194
00:18:21,090 --> 00:18:22,590
To máš na modriny.

195
00:18:24,320 --> 00:18:27,390
Nebuď dojatý, nie je to odomňa.
Posiela to Yeok-Ho.

196
00:18:29,330 --> 00:18:31,730
-A tiež --
-Hej, už bežím do bufetu.

197
00:18:31,730 --> 00:18:33,900
Na to zabudni!
Za koho ma máš?

198
00:18:35,700 --> 00:18:36,730
Bež dovnútra.

199
00:18:39,570 --> 00:18:40,900
Ktože sa nám tu ukázal.

200
00:18:42,740 --> 00:18:45,410
Sebecký zbabelec.

201
00:18:49,250 --> 00:18:50,910
Prečo tu je toľko múch?

202
00:18:54,520 --> 00:18:57,720
O čom hovorí?
Stalo sa niečo?

203
00:18:59,790 --> 00:19:02,130
Vôbec neviem.

204
00:19:22,580 --> 00:19:23,780
Jeong-Woo.

205
00:19:25,350 --> 00:19:26,450
Znova sa stretávame.

206
00:19:34,360 --> 00:19:36,690
Skláňam sa nad tvojou odvahou.

207
00:19:37,960 --> 00:19:41,370
Ale prečo ti to vlastne hovorím?

208
00:19:44,040 --> 00:19:45,670
Už si to začal,

209
00:19:47,340 --> 00:19:48,510
tak to aj dokonči.

210
00:19:50,140 --> 00:19:52,980
Povedal si, nech vypadnem.
Tak som to spravil.

211
00:19:54,510 --> 00:19:55,550
Môj zlatý.

212
00:19:57,150 --> 00:20:00,550
To si taký naivný, či len blbý?

213
00:20:01,690 --> 00:20:02,690
Počuj, hlupáčik môj.

214
00:20:03,250 --> 00:20:06,460
Proste si zdrhol, lebo si sa bál.

215
00:20:08,590 --> 00:20:10,360
Veď sa jej opýtaj,

216
00:20:11,200 --> 00:20:13,900
aký majú s Lee Yeok-Hom vzťah.

217
00:20:16,330 --> 00:20:18,340
Robíš si zo mňa srandu, však?

218
00:20:18,340 --> 00:20:20,940
No teda, ty debil jeden malý...

219
00:20:25,580 --> 00:20:28,850
Len si udri.
Nech nás oboch vyhodia.

220
00:20:29,750 --> 00:20:30,810
Buď ticho.

221
00:20:32,480 --> 00:20:36,850
O čom nemám hovoriť?
O vyhadzove? Či Ah-Yeong?

222
00:20:40,660 --> 00:20:41,890
To je ale zaujímavé.

223
00:20:42,560 --> 00:20:44,390
Vždy, keď ju spomeniem...

224
00:20:52,100 --> 00:20:53,240
Hej, Won-Il.

225
00:20:54,470 --> 00:20:57,570
Je mi jedno, že si ma zapredal Farebným.

226
00:20:58,680 --> 00:21:02,050
No ešte raz vyslovíš jej meno a zabijem ťa.

227
00:21:22,230 --> 00:21:23,730
Dnes máš šťastie.

228
00:21:47,130 --> 00:21:49,830
Oppa, vieš...

229
00:21:50,400 --> 00:21:51,760
Už znova si tu?

230
00:22:02,310 --> 00:22:03,770
Zasa sa na to pozeráš?

231
00:22:09,550 --> 00:22:10,610
Poďme sa prejsť.

232
00:22:18,290 --> 00:22:19,390
Won-Il

233
00:22:20,490 --> 00:22:22,330
ťa ešte stále otravuje?

234
00:22:23,030 --> 00:22:25,330
Čo?
Nie.

235
00:22:26,030 --> 00:22:27,130
Prečo?

236
00:22:30,540 --> 00:22:31,570
Len tak.

237
00:22:38,880 --> 00:22:42,480
Trápi ťa niečo?

238
00:22:50,120 --> 00:22:51,920
To, o čom som ti vravela...

239
00:22:53,890 --> 00:22:56,390
Myslela som, že až na konci roka.

240
00:22:57,960 --> 00:22:59,160
No nie je to tak.

241
00:23:04,770 --> 00:23:05,840
Aha.

242
00:23:06,200 --> 00:23:07,340
Mama vraví,

243
00:23:08,510 --> 00:23:10,610
že je to pre moje vzdelanie.

244
00:23:12,440 --> 00:23:14,750
No podľa mňa je pre rodinu ťažké

245
00:23:17,280 --> 00:23:19,550
žiť tu bez brata.

246
00:23:24,820 --> 00:23:26,360
Už je to rok?

247
00:23:27,860 --> 00:23:28,930
Áno.

248
00:23:53,650 --> 00:23:55,690
<i>Mám právo to vedieť.</i>

249
00:23:57,720 --> 00:24:01,890
Neviem, či si to zaslúžiš vedieť.

250
00:24:01,890 --> 00:24:05,060
No a čo ty?
Ty máš na to aké právo?

251
00:24:05,060 --> 00:24:07,160
Si Ah-Yeongin brat alebo čo?

252
00:24:13,870 --> 00:24:14,940
Choi Jeong-Woo.

253
00:24:16,870 --> 00:24:21,040
Ak si tu ako jej priateľ,
tak nespomínaj práva,

254
00:24:21,050 --> 00:24:23,950
skôr mysli na to, ako dobre ju poznáš.

255
00:24:32,920 --> 00:24:34,760
Ale na tom už vôbec nezáleží.

256
00:24:41,900 --> 00:24:43,630
Našu bitku

257
00:24:48,440 --> 00:24:51,710
už viac neodďaľujme.

258
00:24:55,350 --> 00:24:56,650
Vidíme sa po škole.

259
00:25:04,820 --> 00:25:06,490
Dnes nie sú žiadne stretnutia.

260
00:25:06,490 --> 00:25:09,230
Bude pršať, takže sa večerná škola ruší.

261
00:25:09,230 --> 00:25:11,760
-Pred odchodom si upracte, dobre?
-Jasné.

262
00:25:13,000 --> 00:25:14,030
Oh, ešte počkaj.

263
00:25:14,670 --> 00:25:16,330
Keď skončíš, zastav sa u mňa.

264
00:25:16,900 --> 00:25:17,870
Iste.

265
00:25:21,470 --> 00:25:24,070
Deje sa niečo?

266
00:25:24,080 --> 00:25:25,210
Nedeje.

267
00:25:27,450 --> 00:25:28,550
Ah-Yeong.

268
00:25:31,920 --> 00:25:34,220
Ah-Yeong, po škole --

269
00:25:34,220 --> 00:25:37,120
Po vyučku musím ísť za učiteľkou.
Choď bezo mňa.

270
00:25:40,490 --> 00:25:41,560
Dobre.

271
00:26:09,150 --> 00:26:12,290
Si hladný?
Nič si nezjedol.

272
00:26:14,660 --> 00:26:15,830
Nie som.

273
00:26:16,890 --> 00:26:17,890
Vystrašil si ma.

274
00:26:19,330 --> 00:26:20,360
Hej!

275
00:26:21,470 --> 00:26:23,700
Ticho buďte.

276
00:26:24,470 --> 00:26:25,500
Choi Jeong-Woo.

277
00:26:44,790 --> 00:26:47,420
Čo sa deje?
Prečo ide za Grizlym?

278
00:26:47,430 --> 00:26:49,090
Asi ho už vyzval.

279
00:27:00,500 --> 00:27:01,600
Počkať.

280
00:27:02,540 --> 00:27:04,240
Nemôžeš ich zastaviť?

281
00:27:04,240 --> 00:27:05,880
Jeong-Woo sa bude biť kvôli mne.

282
00:27:05,880 --> 00:27:07,210
Nepleť sa do toho.

283
00:27:07,210 --> 00:27:08,780
Prečo zachádzaš tak ďaleko?

284
00:27:11,080 --> 00:27:12,350
Čo to s vami je?

285
00:27:12,980 --> 00:27:16,720
Celá škola o ich súboji vie.

286
00:27:16,720 --> 00:27:19,690
A čo má najlepší bitkár
v Namile ostať ticho sedieť?

287
00:27:20,320 --> 00:27:21,320
Há?

288
00:27:25,660 --> 00:27:26,960
Poďme dozadu.

289
00:27:28,630 --> 00:27:33,340
Yeok-Ho má niečo v pláne.
Kľud, decká.

290
00:27:33,970 --> 00:27:35,070
Okej?

291
00:27:42,310 --> 00:27:44,710
Grizly a Choi Jeong-Woo sa idú biť!

292
00:27:45,650 --> 00:27:47,150
Bitka!
Bitka!

293
00:27:52,960 --> 00:27:55,690
Vážne?
To je úžasné.

294
00:27:57,360 --> 00:27:59,500
Vráť sa do triedy.

295
00:28:00,600 --> 00:28:03,030
Ty sa nezľakneš,
keď sa vidíš v zrkadle?

296
00:28:25,160 --> 00:28:26,990
Keďže si so mnou šiel až sem,

297
00:28:27,990 --> 00:28:29,930
vidno, že dodržíš slovo.

298
00:28:30,930 --> 00:28:31,800
Čo?

299
00:28:31,800 --> 00:28:33,800
Aj ja som ho musel dodržať,

300
00:28:34,600 --> 00:28:36,530
preto som ťa zavolal von.

301
00:28:37,370 --> 00:28:39,840
<i>Takže to znamená...</i>

302
00:28:41,170 --> 00:28:43,670
Čo hovorí?
Nepočujem ich.

303
00:28:46,880 --> 00:28:48,610
Ak sa ešte raz pobijem,

304
00:28:49,880 --> 00:28:51,680
neprejdem skúškami.

305
00:28:53,450 --> 00:28:55,090
<i>Vďakabohu.</i>

306
00:29:00,560 --> 00:29:01,590
Ale

307
00:29:04,960 --> 00:29:06,400
vidí nás priveľa ľudí.

308
00:29:07,730 --> 00:29:09,530
Takže čosi urobiť musíme.

309
00:29:09,530 --> 00:29:10,630
<i>Čože?</i>

310
00:29:12,200 --> 00:29:13,370
Tak teda

311
00:29:23,380 --> 00:29:27,980
príď v sobotu do telocvične.
Budeme boxovať.

312
00:29:30,620 --> 00:29:31,650
Čo?

313
00:29:31,660 --> 00:29:34,590
Prehrá ten, kto sa vzdá ako prvý.

314
00:29:35,860 --> 00:29:40,430
Ale ak ja čo i len raz
spadnem, vyhrávaš ty.

315
00:29:40,430 --> 00:29:41,530
Okej?

316
00:29:45,340 --> 00:29:46,370
Uvidíme sa.

317
00:29:51,510 --> 00:29:54,080
Nunčaky sa v boxe nepoužívajú.

318
00:29:57,950 --> 00:29:59,420
Ani to.

319
00:30:08,130 --> 00:30:11,860
V sobotu budú mať súboj v boxe.

320
00:30:12,260 --> 00:30:14,560
Nech už je sobota!

321
00:30:21,940 --> 00:30:23,370
Vie on vôbec boxovať?

322
00:30:38,220 --> 00:30:39,790
Nemal si na mňa čakať.

323
00:30:40,520 --> 00:30:42,190
Nie, v pohode.
Však som ani nečakal.

324
00:30:42,890 --> 00:30:44,760
Dobre.
Ďakujem.

325
00:30:47,130 --> 00:30:50,600
Ah-Yeong, vtedy cez prestávku...

326
00:30:52,070 --> 00:30:53,270
Čo?

327
00:30:57,940 --> 00:30:59,040
Ale nič.

328
00:31:03,080 --> 00:31:05,320
Čo robíš zajtra po škole?

329
00:31:05,920 --> 00:31:07,350
Asi sa budem učiť.

330
00:31:08,590 --> 00:31:10,920
Jáj, vlastne zajtra niečo mám.

331
00:31:13,660 --> 00:31:14,790
S Grizlym?

332
00:31:19,830 --> 00:31:23,770
Budeme mať súboj.

333
00:31:26,170 --> 00:31:27,270
Ja viem.

334
00:31:29,110 --> 00:31:30,970
Nechceš mi náhodou niečo povedať?

335
00:31:36,350 --> 00:31:39,820
Povedz mi to.
Čo k nemu cítiš?

336
00:31:41,620 --> 00:31:42,820
Prečo ťa to zaujíma?

337
00:31:43,420 --> 00:31:46,060
Ty sa s ním akože pobiješ kvôli mne?

338
00:31:46,060 --> 00:31:47,660
Prečo mi to nemôžeš povedať?

339
00:31:54,330 --> 00:31:58,640
Zdá sa, že ste si blízki, no
v škole sa spolu vôbec nebavíte.

340
00:31:58,640 --> 00:32:00,370
-A tiež --
-Poznáš Lee Won-Ila?

341
00:32:00,840 --> 00:32:04,310
Stále za mnou liezol.

342
00:32:04,310 --> 00:32:07,280
A Yeok-Ho mi pomohol sa ho zbaviť.
Stačí?

343
00:32:09,650 --> 00:32:14,680
Bolo také ťažké mi to povedať?

344
00:32:14,690 --> 00:32:16,590
Toľkokrát som sa ťa
na Grizlyho pýtal.

345
00:32:16,590 --> 00:32:17,590
Jeong-Woo!

346
00:32:19,160 --> 00:32:22,360
Môžeš ho prestať volať "Grizly"?

347
00:32:27,830 --> 00:32:31,800
A prečo ťa to vlastne zaujíma?

348
00:32:52,120 --> 00:32:53,690
Ešte aj počasie je na nič.

349
00:33:03,730 --> 00:33:04,770
Jeong-Woo.

350
00:33:10,940 --> 00:33:11,940
Čau.

351
00:33:16,050 --> 00:33:19,250
V Yeongdongu prší, len sa leje...

352
00:33:19,250 --> 00:33:20,950
Už sme v Yeongdongu?

353
00:33:21,750 --> 00:33:22,890
Leje jak z krhly.

354
00:33:39,600 --> 00:33:43,510
Vonku leje.
Kam to dieťa zmizlo?

355
00:33:49,750 --> 00:33:52,450
Mal si povedať, že po mňa prídeš.

356
00:33:52,450 --> 00:33:53,480
Eh?

357
00:33:53,480 --> 00:33:56,790
Učiteľka klavíra kvôli mne nešla domov.

358
00:33:58,260 --> 00:34:00,320
Zasa si bol vonku?

359
00:34:00,320 --> 00:34:02,830
Je mi to jasné.

360
00:34:03,990 --> 00:34:06,260
Na takého štupľa príliš veľa kecáš.

361
00:34:07,130 --> 00:34:09,100
Daj ten dáždnik inak.
Prší na mňa.

362
00:34:10,070 --> 00:34:11,530
Nič nevidím.

363
00:34:13,200 --> 00:34:14,270
Čo to?

364
00:34:15,710 --> 00:34:16,740
Drž sa!

365
00:34:20,680 --> 00:34:21,680
Drž sa!

366
00:34:42,930 --> 00:34:45,670
Môžem ísť domov aj pešo.

367
00:34:46,440 --> 00:34:48,840
Nie, prosím ťa.
Veď prší.

368
00:34:49,740 --> 00:34:50,840
Ale aj tak...

369
00:34:55,910 --> 00:34:57,450
-Pomoc!
-Čo sa tam deje?

370
00:35:01,220 --> 00:35:02,320
Pomôžte!

371
00:35:04,820 --> 00:35:06,060
-Dedko!
-Bežme tam.

372
00:35:07,890 --> 00:35:08,930
Dedko!

373
00:35:12,500 --> 00:35:13,660
Vydrž!

374
00:35:17,000 --> 00:35:18,200
Pomóc!

375
00:35:21,310 --> 00:35:22,510
Pomôžte!

376
00:35:24,740 --> 00:35:25,940
Tu!

377
00:35:34,990 --> 00:35:36,690
Si v pohode?

378
00:35:37,550 --> 00:35:38,590
Ako ti je?

379
00:35:39,860 --> 00:35:40,890
Nič ti nie je?

380
00:35:41,860 --> 00:35:44,230
Kde je Yeong-Mi?

381
00:35:44,230 --> 00:35:45,960
-Kde je Yeong-Mi?
-Yeong-Mi?

382
00:35:46,860 --> 00:35:47,700
Yeong-Mi!

383
00:35:48,270 --> 00:35:49,400
Yeong-Bok!

384
00:35:50,530 --> 00:35:52,070
Pomoc!

385
00:35:52,070 --> 00:35:53,170
-Je tam!
-Yeong-Bok!

386
00:35:53,170 --> 00:35:54,470
-Yeong-Mi!
-Nie!

387
00:35:54,470 --> 00:35:55,470
Nie!

388
00:35:57,670 --> 00:35:59,810
Treba dlhší konár.

389
00:35:59,810 --> 00:36:01,340
-Yeong-Mi!
-To nemôžeš.

390
00:36:01,350 --> 00:36:02,910
-Yeong-Mi!
-Prestaň!

391
00:36:02,910 --> 00:36:04,510
Pusti ma!

392
00:36:04,520 --> 00:36:05,780
Nesmieš tam ísť!

393
00:36:07,680 --> 00:36:08,890
Pusti ma!

394
00:36:11,760 --> 00:36:12,860
Yeong-Bok!

395
00:36:14,090 --> 00:36:15,990
-Yeong-Mi!
-Vydrž tam!

396
00:36:17,490 --> 00:36:18,660
-Jeong-Woo!
-Pomoc!

397
00:36:18,660 --> 00:36:21,200
Toto si dám okolo seba, drž ma.

398
00:36:21,200 --> 00:36:23,100
Čože?
Je to nebezpečné!

399
00:36:23,100 --> 00:36:25,170
Ona je vo väčšom nebezpečenstve.

400
00:36:25,170 --> 00:36:26,540
Hej, Deok-Won!
Hej!

401
00:36:31,410 --> 00:36:32,340
Deok-Won!

402
00:36:32,340 --> 00:36:33,580
Yeong-Bok!

403
00:36:36,950 --> 00:36:38,280
Pomoc!

404
00:36:39,780 --> 00:36:42,180
-Pomôžte!
-Pozor, chyť sa ho!

405
00:36:42,190 --> 00:36:43,590
Bojím sa!

406
00:36:44,690 --> 00:36:45,990
Deok-Won!
Vylez!

407
00:36:45,990 --> 00:36:48,120
Musíte mi malú zachrániť!

408
00:36:48,890 --> 00:36:50,030
-Pozor!
-Ešte trochu.

409
00:36:50,890 --> 00:36:52,530
Yeong-Mi!
Chyť sa ho!

410
00:36:55,030 --> 00:36:56,330
Yeong-Bok!

411
00:36:58,370 --> 00:36:59,440
Yeong-Bok!

412
00:37:07,680 --> 00:37:08,780
Yeong-Mi!

413
00:37:10,480 --> 00:37:11,410
Pomoc!

414
00:37:23,130 --> 00:37:24,160
Chyť sa!

415
00:37:25,600 --> 00:37:26,660
Rýchlo!

416
00:37:28,830 --> 00:37:30,170
Už ste v bezpečí.

417
00:37:30,170 --> 00:37:32,670
-Deok-Won!
-Dobre, ešte trochu.

418
00:37:33,140 --> 00:37:34,140
Držte sa.

419
00:37:34,810 --> 00:37:36,170
Yeong-Bok!

420
00:37:37,910 --> 00:37:38,980
Deok-Won!

421
00:37:46,620 --> 00:37:47,680
Yeong-Mi.

422
00:37:48,690 --> 00:37:51,050
-Deok-Won.
-Ešte trochu.

423
00:37:55,560 --> 00:37:56,830
Si v poriadku?

424
00:37:56,830 --> 00:37:58,890
-Nie je ti nič?
-Yeong-Bok!

425
00:37:58,900 --> 00:37:59,900
Deok-Won.

426
00:38:00,600 --> 00:38:02,160
Ty idiot.

427
00:38:02,930 --> 00:38:06,040
Si v pohode?
Bolí ťa niečo?

428
00:38:06,770 --> 00:38:08,370
Hej, ty idiot!

429
00:38:08,370 --> 00:38:09,840
Si v poriadku?

430
00:38:09,840 --> 00:38:10,970
Nezranila si sa?

431
00:38:11,840 --> 00:38:12,980
Som v pohode.

432
00:38:12,980 --> 00:38:14,380
Prepáč mi.
Prepáč mi, moja.

433
00:38:48,180 --> 00:38:49,210
Ah-Yeong.

434
00:39:10,230 --> 00:39:13,440
Včera sa stala na moste nehoda.

435
00:39:13,440 --> 00:39:16,510
Veľa pršalo a voda podmyla základy.

436
00:39:17,010 --> 00:39:20,210
Ale boli tam Deok-Won a Jeong-Woo

437
00:39:21,950 --> 00:39:24,510
a tých ľudí zachránili.

438
00:39:24,510 --> 00:39:29,090
Deok-Won je ešte v nemocnici a Jeong-Woo...

439
00:39:41,230 --> 00:39:43,430
Jeong-Woo, si v poriadku?

440
00:39:46,000 --> 00:39:46,900
Hej.

441
00:39:46,900 --> 00:39:49,240
Zatlieksajme mu.

442
00:39:53,410 --> 00:39:54,440
To je skvelé.

443
00:39:56,550 --> 00:40:00,780
Vyzeráš byť úplne v pohode.
Ako to, že ti nič nie je?

444
00:40:01,380 --> 00:40:04,220
Deok-Won ani nemôže prísť, a ty...

445
00:40:14,560 --> 00:40:15,800
Yeong-Bok.

446
00:40:16,970 --> 00:40:18,030
Čau.

447
00:40:19,800 --> 00:40:20,840
Poď sem.

448
00:40:21,740 --> 00:40:22,810
Na.

449
00:40:25,240 --> 00:40:28,180
To je pre Deok-Wona.

450
00:40:28,810 --> 00:40:31,510
Aj ty si daj.

451
00:40:33,120 --> 00:40:34,150
A tiež...

452
00:40:39,360 --> 00:40:41,020
Ale nič.
No bež.

453
00:40:50,770 --> 00:40:52,000
<i>Zabúdal som,</i>

454
00:40:52,870 --> 00:40:56,270
<i>kým skutočne som.</i>

455
00:40:58,040 --> 00:41:01,610
<i>Asi som jediný,</i>

456
00:41:01,610 --> 00:41:03,180
<i>kto sa nezmenil.</i>

457
00:41:22,330 --> 00:41:25,870
Prečo chodíš za takým starým dedom?

458
00:41:29,110 --> 00:41:30,640
Dám ti niečo pod zub.

459
00:41:32,280 --> 00:41:35,110
Nie, sadnite si.
Ja to urobím.

460
00:41:54,100 --> 00:41:55,970
Poznáš môjho vnuka, však?

461
00:41:56,570 --> 00:42:00,500
Je silný, takže je v škole
celkom populárny.

462
00:42:01,100 --> 00:42:04,270
<i>Hej, toho teda poznám.</i>

463
00:42:05,180 --> 00:42:08,440
Vychovával som ho,
odkedy mu zomreli rodičia.

464
00:42:08,510 --> 00:42:12,450
Takže navonok je tvrdý,

465
00:42:12,720 --> 00:42:14,780
no má dobré srdce.

466
00:42:19,620 --> 00:42:22,690
Hej, hej.
Budem jesť.

467
00:42:23,460 --> 00:42:27,060
Neboj sa o mňa.
Hlavne si daj pozor.

468
00:42:27,760 --> 00:42:29,630
Hej.

469
00:42:29,630 --> 00:42:30,770
Ako sa to volá?

470
00:42:32,400 --> 00:42:34,070
Jasné, Ah-Yeong.

471
00:42:35,640 --> 00:42:37,710
Kúp jej niečo dobré.

472
00:42:38,340 --> 00:42:40,440
Neboj sa o mňa.

473
00:43:04,630 --> 00:43:07,240
[Yang Yeong-Wung]
[30.10.1985 - 7.6.2002]

474
00:43:15,280 --> 00:43:19,680
Tak predsa nie si úplne naničhodný.

475
00:43:20,820 --> 00:43:21,850
Prosím?

476
00:43:43,210 --> 00:43:46,140
Poznáte tohto chalana?

477
00:43:54,180 --> 00:43:56,020
Dobré!
Pekné!

478
00:43:56,020 --> 00:43:57,050
To je ono!

479
00:43:57,590 --> 00:44:00,560
Prečo tieto päste márniš v gangu?

480
00:44:01,420 --> 00:44:02,860
Dobre, ideme.

481
00:44:02,860 --> 00:44:06,000
Raz, dva.
Je to sľub, okej?

482
00:44:06,000 --> 00:44:08,360
Tieto päste sa už deciek nedotknú.

483
00:44:09,330 --> 00:44:10,470
Dobre.

484
00:44:10,470 --> 00:44:15,840
<i>Vďaka nemu sa Yeok-Ho prestal biť.</i>

485
00:44:16,610 --> 00:44:18,110
<i>Bol to skvelý chalan.</i>

486
00:44:18,810 --> 00:44:19,840
Hej.

487
00:44:19,840 --> 00:44:21,110
Ah-Yeong.

488
00:44:27,150 --> 00:44:27,580
-Hej.
-Prestaň.

489
00:44:27,580 --> 00:44:28,650
S čím?

490
00:44:28,650 --> 00:44:29,790
S ničím.

491
00:44:29,790 --> 00:44:31,750
-Čo chcete?
-Vraví, že si zlatá.

492
00:44:36,190 --> 00:44:37,990
Tebe sa tak s niečím zveriť.

493
00:44:40,760 --> 00:44:43,070
Počuj, toto si žičnem.

494
00:44:43,830 --> 00:44:45,130
Chcem si to vziať na stanovačku.

495
00:44:46,400 --> 00:44:49,540
Môžem ísť s tebou?

496
00:44:49,540 --> 00:44:52,040
Nie, počkaj, až budeš na rade.

497
00:44:52,710 --> 00:44:55,980
Je to posledný výlet pred profi skúškami.
ty tam pôjdeš budúci rok.

498
00:44:59,950 --> 00:45:03,620
<i>Po nedávnom zvýšení hladiny riek</i>

499
00:45:03,620 --> 00:45:06,620
<i>zostalo mnoho ľudí nezvestných.</i>

500
00:45:06,620 --> 00:45:09,790
<i>Veľa z nich sú študenti
nižších aj vyšších stredných škôl,</i>

501
00:45:09,790 --> 00:45:12,960
<i>ako aj univerzít.</i>

502
00:45:13,560 --> 00:45:16,100
<i>Tu je aktuálny zoznam obetí.</i>

503
00:45:16,100 --> 00:45:20,100
<i>Kim Min-Ju, Lee Eun-Gi, Park Ah-Yeong,</i>

504
00:45:20,100 --> 00:45:22,970
<i>Kim Ji-Hun, Yang Yeong-Wung.</i>

505
00:45:24,370 --> 00:45:27,440
<i>Podľa svedkov Yang Yeong-Wunga strhol prúd,</i>

506
00:45:27,440 --> 00:45:32,080
<i>keď zachraňoval topiace sa dieťa.</i>

507
00:45:32,680 --> 00:45:36,950
<i>Jedno zachránil a vracal sa po druhé,</i>

508
00:45:36,950 --> 00:45:39,890
<i>keď ho prúd strhol so sebou.</i>

509
00:46:36,410 --> 00:46:40,620
Možno to nevidieť, no Ah-Yeong je silná.

510
00:46:41,780 --> 00:46:44,390
Pred inými ľuďmi nikdy neplače.

511
00:46:44,390 --> 00:46:45,890
Vždy taká bola.

512
00:46:46,490 --> 00:46:48,490
Keď je osamote, reve ako krokodíl.

513
00:47:26,360 --> 00:47:27,960
Štastnú cestu.

514
00:47:27,960 --> 00:47:29,160
Ďakujem.
Dobrú noc.

515
00:48:20,180 --> 00:48:23,050
Bež do postele.
Iste si unavený.

516
00:48:23,920 --> 00:48:26,520
Ty si pospi.
Pôjdem si zabehať.

517
00:48:48,140 --> 00:48:52,150
Priniesol mi to ten mládenec.

518
00:48:53,450 --> 00:48:56,390
On to ževraj jedáva, keď je chorý.

519
00:48:56,390 --> 00:48:59,550
Vraj mu to dá silu tigra alebo čo.

520
00:49:30,220 --> 00:49:31,790
Ďakujem, že ste prišli.

521
00:49:33,190 --> 00:49:34,560
Ahojte.

522
00:49:34,560 --> 00:49:35,660
Hyung.

523
00:49:39,060 --> 00:49:40,160
Eh?

524
00:49:41,100 --> 00:49:42,800
Dedko, dedko...

525
00:49:44,000 --> 00:49:46,340
nemohol si ešte chvíľu počkať?

526
00:49:46,400 --> 00:49:49,540
Aspoň dokým sa Yeok-Ho
neožení a nezaloží si rodinu.

527
00:49:51,270 --> 00:49:53,340
Choi Jeong-Woo, tak dlho sme sa nevideli.

528
00:49:53,340 --> 00:49:55,540
Ako to, že máš toľko práce?
Skoro vôbec sa nevídame.

529
00:49:57,550 --> 00:49:58,910
Tak to vyšlo.

530
00:49:58,920 --> 00:50:03,720
Už neplytvaj časom a ožeň sa.

531
00:50:03,720 --> 00:50:06,690
Vnúčatá sú pre rodičov ten najväčší dar.

532
00:50:06,690 --> 00:50:09,490
Akoby si ty deti mal.

533
00:50:11,330 --> 00:50:12,630
On je totálne mimo.

534
00:50:14,960 --> 00:50:17,430
Yeong-Bokovi sa o mesiac narodí druhé.

535
00:50:17,430 --> 00:50:18,630
Budú to dvojičky.

536
00:50:20,370 --> 00:50:21,440
Fakt?

537
00:50:25,780 --> 00:50:27,910
Všetci vyzeráte rovnako.

538
00:50:28,810 --> 00:50:30,910
A máte rodiny.

539
00:50:30,910 --> 00:50:34,120
Jeong-Woo, síce si nebol práve kulturista,

540
00:50:34,120 --> 00:50:36,750
no mal si odvahu.
Čo sa ti to stalo?

541
00:50:37,290 --> 00:50:39,650
Presne, on sa ničoho nebál.

542
00:50:39,660 --> 00:50:41,020
-Hej.
-Spomínaš si?

543
00:50:41,420 --> 00:50:43,630
Šielaj proti najväčšiemu
bitkárovi mesta, Lee Yeok-Hovi

544
00:50:43,630 --> 00:50:46,430
-Jeong-Woo bol teda niečo.
-Trochu rešpektu by nezaškodilo!

545
00:50:47,800 --> 00:50:51,030
Kam všetka tá odvaha zmizla?

546
00:50:52,640 --> 00:50:57,210
Teraz som len obyčajný
chlapík, čo hľadá prácu.

547
00:50:58,210 --> 00:51:00,640
Máš priateľku?

548
00:51:01,410 --> 00:51:03,040
No iste.

549
00:51:03,050 --> 00:51:06,080
Si stále sám, lebo si ešte nezabudol

550
00:51:06,080 --> 00:51:07,350
na svoju prvú lásku?

551
00:51:07,350 --> 00:51:10,820
Hej, ktorá sa ti to vtedy páčila?

552
00:51:10,820 --> 00:51:12,990
Vaša predsedkyňa triedy.
Tá múdra.

553
00:51:12,990 --> 00:51:14,890
Ako sa volala?
Yang...

554
00:51:14,890 --> 00:51:16,860
-Yang Ah-Yeong.
-Yang Ah-Yeong.

555
00:51:16,860 --> 00:51:18,430
Dal som to prvý.

556
00:51:21,300 --> 00:51:22,900
Počul si

557
00:51:25,440 --> 00:51:26,800
o nej niečo?

558
00:51:40,420 --> 00:51:43,750
Predsedkyňa, ide sa do telocvične.
Čo tu robíš?

559
00:51:44,920 --> 00:51:46,720
Eh?
Aha.

560
00:51:59,670 --> 00:52:00,740
Tak ja pôjdem.

561
00:52:10,980 --> 00:52:13,650
Ja poviem "Choi" a vy "Jeong-Woo"!

562
00:52:13,650 --> 00:52:17,150
-Choi!
-Jeong-Woo!

563
00:52:20,860 --> 00:52:22,790
Jeong-Woo!

564
00:52:23,530 --> 00:52:26,130
-Veľa štastia.
-Budeš v pohode?

565
00:52:26,130 --> 00:52:28,330
-Ideš na to.
-To dáš.

566
00:52:39,640 --> 00:52:40,680
Si v pohode?

567
00:52:47,380 --> 00:52:51,090
Vyzeráš desivo.
Nebuď naňho tvrdý.

568
00:52:53,720 --> 00:52:54,960
[Si naša jediná šanca]

569
00:52:55,160 --> 00:52:56,630
[Jeong-Woo]
[Zlož ho]

570
00:53:08,070 --> 00:53:09,400
Jeong-Woo, dávaj pozor.

571
00:53:22,320 --> 00:53:24,250
-Keď budeš unavený, povedz.
-Pozor!

572
00:53:24,250 --> 00:53:25,520
Povedz, ak si unavený.

573
00:53:27,490 --> 00:53:29,320
Prečo sa rovno nevzdáš?

574
00:53:34,960 --> 00:53:36,400
V pohode?

575
00:53:36,400 --> 00:53:37,770
Toto nie je dobrý nápad.

576
00:53:39,470 --> 00:53:42,100
Za chvíľu skončí prvé kolo!
Ešte vydrž.

577
00:53:42,100 --> 00:53:44,170
To dáš.

578
00:53:44,170 --> 00:53:46,340
Skvele sa úderom vyhýba.

579
00:53:52,650 --> 00:53:53,680
Len kľud.

580
00:53:56,320 --> 00:53:57,790
Buď stále v pozore.

581
00:54:09,900 --> 00:54:11,400
[Prepáč mi to]

582
00:54:20,080 --> 00:54:21,510
Jeong-Woo alebo Grizly?

583
00:54:21,510 --> 00:54:24,550
Hej, tu.
Dobrý výber.

584
00:54:24,550 --> 00:54:25,710
-Kto ešte?
-Aj ja.

585
00:54:25,720 --> 00:54:28,220
Dobrý výber, chlape.

586
00:54:28,220 --> 00:54:29,680
Jeong-Woo.
-Super!

587
00:54:32,790 --> 00:54:34,320
Nerob to, ak si unavený.

588
00:54:38,860 --> 00:54:40,160
<i>Si hrdina.</i>

589
00:54:41,160 --> 00:54:42,330
<i>Hrdina Namilskej strednej.</i>

590
00:54:51,770 --> 00:54:54,110
<i>Ak si tu ako jej priateľ,
tak nespomínaj práva,</i>

591
00:54:54,110 --> 00:54:56,850
skôr mysli na to, ako dobre ju poznáš.

592
00:55:04,350 --> 00:55:05,450
Boj!

593
00:55:23,310 --> 00:55:24,940
Otočka!
Skrč sa!

594
00:55:29,810 --> 00:55:31,310
Otoč sa!
Skrč sa!

595
00:55:37,690 --> 00:55:41,020
<i>Hrať sa že nevidím,
nepočujem, nevšímam si.</i>

596
00:55:42,590 --> 00:55:44,130
<i>Takto som chcel žiť.</i>

597
00:55:50,770 --> 00:55:53,070
-<i>Bolo by mi jedno, ak by som</i>
-Si v poho?

598
00:55:53,900 --> 00:55:55,870
-Dávaj pozor!
-<i>...potom bol za slabocha.</i>

599
00:55:57,770 --> 00:56:00,040
Nie!
Pusti ho!

600
00:56:04,580 --> 00:56:05,680
<i>Yang Ah-Yeong.</i>

601
00:56:07,180 --> 00:56:09,820
<i>Nemal som na ňu vtedy zavolať.</i>

602
00:56:09,820 --> 00:56:14,320
Choi Jeong-Woo!
Choi Jeong-Woo!

603
00:56:25,170 --> 00:56:27,170
<i>Toho dňa sa všetko
obrátilo o 360 stupňov.</i>

604
00:56:32,780 --> 00:56:34,180
<i>Aj moje srdce.</i>

605
00:56:59,670 --> 00:57:01,040
Páči sa ti Ah-Yeong?

606
00:57:05,470 --> 00:57:08,110
Vieš, koho najviac neznášam?

607
00:57:10,650 --> 00:57:11,810
Koho?

608
00:57:17,450 --> 00:57:18,950
Tých, čo stále kecajú.

609
00:57:23,990 --> 00:57:26,430
Nechcem, aby niekoho takého stretla.

610
00:57:40,080 --> 00:57:41,980
Len vydrž!
Už je skoro koniec kola.

611
00:57:57,330 --> 00:57:58,490
Yeok-Ho.

612
00:58:14,940 --> 00:58:17,580
<i>Povedz mi to.
Čo k nemu cítiš?</i>

613
00:58:17,580 --> 00:58:20,050
Bolo také ťažké mi to povedať?
Toľkokrát som sa

614
00:58:20,050 --> 00:58:21,920
ťa na Grizlyho pýtal.
-Jeong-Woo.

615
00:58:23,420 --> 00:58:26,890
Môžeš mu prestať vravieť "Grizly"?

616
00:58:31,490 --> 00:58:32,530
Jeong-Woo.

617
00:58:34,330 --> 00:58:36,060
Jeong-Woo, si v pohode?

618
00:58:37,870 --> 00:58:39,800
Čo robíte?
Počítajte!

619
00:58:40,540 --> 00:58:42,140
Rýchlo, počítajte.

620
00:58:42,140 --> 00:58:46,240
-Ešte to neskončilo.
-Nabok, mladý.

621
00:58:46,240 --> 00:58:47,040
Idete.

622
00:58:47,710 --> 00:58:51,580
Raz, dva, tri, štyri, päť,
šesť, sedem, osem.

623
00:58:53,680 --> 00:58:54,950
Stačí.

624
00:59:06,900 --> 00:59:08,500
Choi Jeong-Woo!

625
00:59:43,870 --> 00:59:46,000
Počítajte!
Rýchlo!

626
00:59:46,000 --> 00:59:47,540
Zdvihni sa.

627
00:59:58,350 --> 00:59:59,680
Takú, čo ma rozveselí.

628
01:00:02,720 --> 01:00:05,920
Môžeš zaspievať niečo, čo ma rozveselí?

629
01:00:08,420 --> 01:00:10,360
Jasné, zaspievam.

630
01:00:13,560 --> 01:00:16,100
Raz, dva, tri, štyri, päť, šesť...

631
01:00:16,100 --> 01:00:17,600
Vstávam.

632
01:00:17,600 --> 01:00:18,400
Jeong-Woo!

633
01:00:19,070 --> 01:00:22,040
Choi Jeong-Woo!

634
01:00:24,270 --> 01:00:25,340
Boj!

635
01:00:41,460 --> 01:00:42,860
Jeong-Woo!

636
01:00:43,530 --> 01:00:44,730
Jeong-Woo!

637
01:00:44,730 --> 01:00:46,930
Jeong-Woo!
Si v poriadku?

638
01:00:47,660 --> 01:00:49,000
Jeong-Woo!

639
01:00:49,770 --> 01:00:51,600
-Dvíhaj sa!
-Jeong-Woo!

640
01:00:53,670 --> 01:00:56,900
Raz, dva, tri, štyri, päť, šesť, sedem...

641
01:00:56,910 --> 01:00:58,210
Pokračujeme!

642
01:01:02,310 --> 01:01:03,380
No do riti.

643
01:01:03,380 --> 01:01:06,610
Jeong-Woo, si v poriadku?

644
01:01:11,890 --> 01:01:15,790
Prečo ťa to zaujíma?

645
01:01:19,230 --> 01:01:23,660
Kiež by si bol zodpovednejší.

646
01:01:38,910 --> 01:01:40,580
Prečo to rovno nevzdáš?

647
01:01:41,950 --> 01:01:44,720
Prečo?
Pretože nás vidí Ah-Yeong?

648
01:01:45,750 --> 01:01:49,320
Nechceš prehrať
pred očami svojej baby?

649
01:01:49,320 --> 01:01:50,690
Ja ani neviem.

650
01:01:51,490 --> 01:01:52,660
Niečo...

651
01:01:54,530 --> 01:01:57,170
je so mnou vážne zle.

652
01:02:01,040 --> 01:02:03,300
Ak ti ide o to, že nás vidí,

653
01:02:03,310 --> 01:02:06,540
tak sa nenechaj udierať.
Udri aj sám.

654
01:02:18,090 --> 01:02:21,260
<i>Už sa nebudem hrať, že nič
nevidím, nepočujem, ani si nevšímam.</i>

655
01:02:24,560 --> 01:02:26,230
<i>Chcem sa ti pozrieť</i>

656
01:02:28,960 --> 01:02:30,630
<i>dôstojne do očí.</i>

